    "gp_section_609042298260816818": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3046a97f8852c2c9623f53b982af326c813cc37b3cb97329a5708337b988cbd3_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_0": "<p>Deep clean. No dry, tight feeling after</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_1": "<p>Dermatologist-tested</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_2": "<p>3.4 fl oz — lasts about 2 months</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_0": "<p>Who’s this for?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1": "<p>Why not just use water?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2": "<p>How to use it</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3": "<p>Pro tip</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4": "<p>Key Ingredients</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5": "<p>Will it dry my skin out?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6": "<p>Shipping</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_7": "<p>60-Day “Try It” Guarantee</p>",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If it doesn’t live up to what we say, you’ve got 60 days to get every dollar back.<br>No hoops. No drama.</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p>Use it before shaving.</p><p>It softens your skin and facial hair so the razor glides easier.<br>Less irritation. Cleaner shave.</p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p>Men who want their face actually clean and ready for whatever they’re putting on next.</p><p>This washes off dirt, oil, sweat, and buildup<br>so your cream or serum can actually do its job.</p><p>Works for all skin types.<br>Dry. Oily. Somewhere in between.</p>",
        "ggLD8D7LMWd_label": "Add to Cart",
        "ggLD8D7LMWd_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggLD8D7LMWd_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggLD8D7LMWd_variantSelectionRequiredMessage": "Please select a variant to add product to cart",
        "ggLuQ0nuQN8_text": "<p>Because water doesn’t cut it.</p><p>Water won’t remove oil, pollution, dead skin, or the junk your face collects all day.</p><p>A real cleanser does.</p><p>Clean skin absorbs products better.<br>Which means better results. Faster.</p>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p><strong>Niacinamide</strong><br>Helps improve skin elasticity.<br>Reduces excess pigment.<br>Helps fade dark spots.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Chamomile</strong><br>Calms irritated skin.<br>Great after shaving.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate</strong><br>Helps your skin hold onto moisture — even after you rinse.<br>So you feel clean. Not dried out.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p><strong>Step 1:</strong><br>2–3 pumps on a wet face</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong><br>Rub in with circular motions</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong><br>Rinse. Dry off. Done.</p>",
        "ggVLmbUDTCI_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:23px;\">Face Cleanser</span></p>",
        "ggWWrnyOmWZ_text": "<p>Ships in 24–48 hours from our Italian warehouse.<br>Free shipping on orders over €50.</p>",
        "ggd3njxJyN7_text": "60-day Guarantee",
        "ggg59nFYXJE_text": "<p>No</p><p>Unlike basic bar soap, this doesn’t strip your skin raw.</p><p>Niacinamide and Chamomile help keep your skin balanced and comfortable.</p><p>Clean — not tight.</p>",
        "ggz0FAMQkBP_text": "<p>You’ve got 60 days to test it.<br>If you don’t like it, email us.<br>You get 100% of your money back.</p>",
        "section_preload": "true"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-609042298260816818"
    },
