        "gg1j4ei5grg_label": "<p><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate</strong></p>",
        "gg2yGs5LDlR_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">AQUA [WATER], DECYL GLUCOSIDE, GLYCERIN, NIACINAMIDE, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, COCAMIDOPROPYL BETAINE, ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF JUICE (), XANTHAN GUM, PHENOXYETHANOL, CHAMOMILLA RECUTITA (MATRICARIA) FLOWER (), SODIUM ASCORBYL PHOSPHATE, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, CITRIC ACID, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, SODIUM HYALURONATE, LINALYL ACETATE, TETRASODIUM GLUTAMATE DIACETATE, LINALOOL, LAVANDULA ANGUSTIFOLIA (LAVENDER) OIL, SODIUM BENZOATE, POTASSIUM SORBATE</span></p>",
        "ggLeqJI7XQW_childItem_0": "<p>Full Ingredient List</p>",
        "ggU84KAzI43_text": "<p>A form of Vitamin B3 that helps your skin act its age — not look older than it is.</p><p>Improves elasticity.<br>Helps fade dark spots.<br>Keeps oil production in check so you’re not shiny by noon.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What it does:</strong><br>• Fades dark spots and uneven tone<br>• Improves skin elasticity<br>• Controls excess oil</p>",
        "ggkvOXZntCM_text": "<p>Italian-sourced ingredients. No filler. No nonsense.</p>",
        "ggq2VeAT1Um_text": "<p>Calms your skin. Especially after shaving.<br>Helps cut down redness and irritation — the natural way.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What it does:</strong><br>• Soothes irritated skin<br>• Reduces post-shave redness<br>• Helps your skin settle down fast</p>",
        "ggtOVHAQdCx_text": "<p>Keeps moisture in your skin even after you rinse.</p><p>So your face feels clean.<br>Not tight. Not dry. Not like you just used bar soap.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What it does:</strong><br>• Hydrates without feeling heavy<br>• Leaves skin soft after washing<br>• No dry, stretched feeling</p>",
        "ggv1U-w8hnC_label": "<p>Chamomile Extract</p>",
        "ggwTMw9UkAs_text": "<span style=\"color:#17162E;\">What your skin actually needs. Nothing else.</span>"
      },
