        "gg2xFSx-IzP_text": "<p><strong>Step 1:</strong><br>2–3 pumps on a wet face</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong><br>Rub in with circular motions</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong><br>Rinse. Dry off. Done.</p>",
        "gg5r67GKkA8_childItem_0": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Can I find it in stores?</span></p>",
