        "ggPeIVTKzHi_text": "<p>No.</p><p>Unlike basic bar soap, this doesn’t strip your skin raw.</p><p>Niacinamide and Chamomile help keep your skin balanced and comfortable.</p><p>Clean — not tight.</p>",
